      <li>
        <strong>Reserved instances reduce costs.</strong> Azure Reserved Instances (1-year or 3-year commitments)
        can reduce compute and database costs by 30-50%. These savings are not reflected in the estimates above
        but should be considered for production workloads beyond the initial engagement.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Data transfer costs excluded.</strong> Egress charges, inter-region transfer, and bandwidth costs
        are not included. For a tool with low external data transfer requirements, these are expected to be
        minimal (&lt;$5/month per tenant).
