    </p>

    <ol class="list-decimal pl-6 mb-4 space-y-2 text-[#2D2D2D]">
      <li>
        <strong>Revert DNS.</strong> Point the tenantid.cloud9consulting.com CNAME back to the original
        single-tenant App Service (still running during the 2-week holding period). Propagation takes &lt;5 minutes.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Disable read-only mode.</strong> Re-enable writes on the single-tenant instance. The tenant
        is back to its original state with no data loss.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>Investigate and retry.</strong> Diagnose the issue using Application Insights logs and the
        multi-tenant staging environment. Fix the root cause and re-attempt migration in the next maintenance window.
      </li>
    </ol>

